'''2013年捷克眾議院选举'''于2013年10月25–26日在[[捷克共和国|捷克]]，而早在7个月前宪法所规定的四年[[捷克众议院|众议院]]议员任期就已届满。

2013年6月17日，[[2010年捷克大选|2010年选举]]后组建的政府总理[[彼得·内恰斯|彼得·内恰斯]]因为腐败和贿赂丑闻而被迫辞职，而之后由总统任命的[[伊日·鲁斯诺克|伊日·鲁斯-{}-诺克]]看守政府在同年8月7日国会信任投票中以微弱票数未获通过，导致6天后看守政府的总辞。<ref name="Caretaker government resigned">{{cite web|url=http://www.europeanvoice.com/article/2013/august/czech-government-resigns/78046.aspx|title=Czech government resigns|publisher=European Voice|date=13 August 2013|accessdate=14 August 2013|archive-date=2013-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131122080428/http://www.europeanvoice.com/article/2013/august/czech-government-resigns/78046.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而众议院则在8月20日通过国会下院自行解散的决议，并于60天内进行眾议院选举，而伊日·鲁斯-{}-诺克政府成为看守内阁并继续运作至新一届下议院组成完毕，<ref name="AP confirmed vote result">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/lawmakers-dissolve-parliaments-lower-house-czech-republic-to-hold-early-election/2013/08/20/adc1cb46-09ae-11e3-89fe-abb4a5067014_story.html|title=Lawmakers dissolve parliament’s lower house, Czech Republic to hold early election|publisher=Washington Post|date=20 August 2013|accessdate=20 August 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130820161354/http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/lawmakers-dissolve-parliaments-lower-house-czech-republic-to-hold-early-election/2013/08/20/adc1cb46-09ae-11e3-89fe-abb4a5067014_story.html|archivedate=2013年8月20日}}</ref><ref name="Parliament approved elections in October">{{cite web|url=http://www.psp.cz/sqw/hlasy.sqw?g=58296&l=cz|title=59th Meeting, 6th voting (20th August 2013, 17:17) on: Draft resolution on the proposal of the President to dissolve the Chamber of Deputies|publisher=Poslanecká Snemovna Parlamentu Ceske Republiky|date=20 August 2013|accessdate=20 August 2013|archive-date=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019083105/http://www.psp.cz/sqw/hlasy.sqw?g=58296&l=cz|dead-url=no}}</ref>众议院选举拟定在2013年10月25–26日进行<ref name="2013 election dates set">{{cite web|url=http://www.radio.cz/en/section/news/news-2013-08-28#1|title=Zeman confirms dissolution of the lower house|publisher=Radio Praha|date=28 August 2013|accessdate=3 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929162752/http://www.radio.cz/en/section/news/news-2013-08-28#1|archivedate=2013-09-29}}</ref>。

==背景==
2010年5月，虽然中左的捷克社民党在[[2010年捷克大选|2010年捷克大选]]中成为第一大政党，但是三个中右政党公民民主党、公众事务党和传统、责任、繁荣党以118席的优势获得了组阁权。议会第二大党党首[[彼得·内恰斯|彼得·内恰斯]]就任新一届[[捷克总理|总理]]。而捷克社民党成为最大的反对党。

2013年6月17日，彼得·内恰斯则在[[2013年捷克打擊組織犯罪行動|2013年打击组织犯罪]]的行动中因牵连其中而辞职。反对党捷克社民党则要求解散众议院，提前举行选举。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ceskenoviny.cz/zpravy/cssd-chce-predcasne-volby-shani-poslance-pro-rozpusteni-snemovny/954381|title=ČSSD chce předčasné volby, shání poslance pro rozpuštění Sněmovny|date=22 June 2013|publisher=České noviny ([[ČTK|ČTK]])|language=cs|accessdate=10 August 2013|archive-date=2019-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191015102815/https://www.ceskenoviny.cz/zpravy/cssd-chce-predcasne-volby-shani-poslance-pro-rozpusteni-snemovny/954381|dead-url=no}}</ref>在众议院仍有98席的中右翼联盟提名Miroslava Němcová为新的总理候选人以便继续维持中右翼政府。但是这还需要获得3个无党籍议员的支持。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://praguemonitor.com/2013/06/20/civic-democrats-agree-n%C4%9Bmcov%C3%A1-their-candidate-prime-minister|title=Civic Democrats agree on Němcová as their candidate for prime minister|publisher=Prague Daily Monitor|date=20 June 2013|accessdate=22 August 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210552/http://praguemonitor.com/2013/06/20/civic-democrats-agree-n%C4%9Bmcov%C3%A1-their-candidate-prime-minister|archivedate=2013年10月29日}}</ref></small><ref name="Minor parties in Chamber of Deputies">{{cite web|url=http://www.tyden.cz/rubriky/domaci/politika/nerozhodnuti-zustavaji-ctyri-poslanci-vlada-prezije-i-tak_273964.html|title=Analýza: Nerozhodnutí zůstávají čtyři poslanci. Vláda přežije i tak. [Analysis: Four MPs remain undecided. The government will survive.]|language=cs|publisher=Tyden.ch|date=20 June 2013|accessdate=22 August 2013|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127021123/https://www.tyden.cz/rubriky/domaci/politika/nerozhodnuti-zustavaji-ctyri-poslanci-vlada-prezije-i-tak_273964.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Parliamentary seats on 25 July 2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.psp.cz/sqw/hlasy.sqw?g=58052&l=cz|title=54th meeting, 90th voting (25th June 2013, 14:09)|publisher=Poslanecká Snemovna Parlamentu Ceske Republiky|date=25 June 2013|accessdate=22 August 2013|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203103604/http://www.psp.cz/sqw/hlasy.sqw?g=58052&l=cz|dead-url=no}}</ref>为了证明信总理候选人能够获得众议院多数，中右翼联盟提交了101名议员有效支持签名（其中包括2名捷克为了人民-自民党、1名无党籍议员）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.denik.cz/z_domova/koalice-predlozila-zemanovi-101-podpisu-poslancu-kteri-podpori-politickou-vladu.html|title=The coalition has 101 signatures for the government led by Nemcova|language=cs|publisher=Denik|date=25 June 2013|accessdate=25 August 2013|archive-date=2019-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190929010942/https://www.denik.cz/z_domova/koalice-predlozila-zemanovi-101-podpisu-poslancu-kteri-podpori-politickou-vladu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>就在这种情况下，总统提名伊日·鲁斯-{}-诺克为看守内阁总理候选人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aktualne.centrum.cz/czechnews/clanek.phtml?id=782606 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029202634/http://aktualne.centrum.cz/czechnews/clanek.phtml?id=782606 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aktualne.centrum.cz/czechnews/clanek.phtml?id=782794 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029202258/http://aktualne.centrum.cz/czechnews/clanek.phtml?id=782794 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://aktualne.centrum.cz/czechnews/clanek.phtml?id=783550 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-10-27 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911231220/https://zpravy.aktualne.cz/zeman-names-caretaker-pm-but-coalition-wants-to-go-on/r~i:article:783550/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>提名前总理[[扬·菲舍尔|扬·菲舍尔]]为看守内阁财政部长。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-08/rusnok-selects-former-premier-fischer-as-czech-finance-minister.html | work=Bloomberg | first1=Peter | last1=Laca | first2=Lenka | last2=Ponikelska | title=Ex-Premier Fischer Selected as Czech Finance Minister | date=8 July 2013 | accessdate=2013-10-27 | archive-date=2013-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029211430/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-08/rusnok-selects-former-premier-fischer-as-czech-finance-minister.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>捷克总统泽曼强调，如果不信任其提出的候选人，他将考虑支持中右翼联盟提名的新总理候选人。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://aktualne.centrum.cz/domaci/politika/clanek.phtml?id=786056|title=Zeman wants ODS and TOP 09 notarized signatures|language=cs|publisher=Aktualne|date=24 July 2013|accessdate=25 August 2013|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201843/http://aktualne.centrum.cz/domaci/politika/clanek.phtml?id=786056|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年8月7日，众议院在对总统提名的看守内阁总理的[[不信任动议|信任投票]]中以93票支持、100票反对、7票弃权的结果下否决了总统的提名，其中起到决定性的是中右翼联盟。<ref name="Rusnok lost confidence vote">{{cite web|url=http://www.psp.cz/sqw/hlasy.sqw?g=58140&l=cz|title=57th Meeting, 11th voting (7th August 2013, 20:53) on: Request Czech government a vote of confidence|publisher=Poslanecká Snemovna Parlamentu Ceske Republiky|date=7 August 2013|accessdate=21 August 2013|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203103604/http://www.psp.cz/sqw/hlasy.sqw?g=58140&l=cz|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年8月20日14:00，在众议院进行众议院正式解散的投票，4个政党（TOP 09、ČSSD、KSČM和VV）计超过140名议员投了赞成票。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rozhlas.cz/zpravy/politika/_zprava/cesko-se-blizi-k-predcasnym-volbam-poslanci-zrejme-schvali-rozpusteni-snemovny--1247678|title=Česko se blíží k předčasným volbám, poslanci zřejmě schválí rozpuštění sněmovny|date=20 August 2013|publisher=[[Czech_Radio|Czech Radio]]|language=cs|accessdate=20 August 2013|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203103604/http://www.rozhlas.cz/zpravy/politika/_zprava/cesko-se-blizi-k-predcasnym-volbam-poslanci-zrejme-schvali-rozpusteni-snemovny--1247678|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.psp.cz/docs/laws/constitution.html|title=Constitution of the Czech Republic (16 December 1992)|language=cs|publisher=Poslanecká Sněmovna Parlament České Republiky|accessdate=2013-10-27|archive-date=2017-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170724093509/http://psp.cz/docs/laws/constitution.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><Ref>
